    <string name="about1">Zazen Meditation Timer — Yon senp revèy meditasyon ak seksyon personnalisable, son klòch, ak jesyon sesyon.</string>
    <string name="about2">Originally kreye pa Stefan Gaffga. Aktyèlman konsève pa Georg Graf.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Mèsi a Winfried nan &lt;a href="http://www.meditationsuhren.de"&gt;http://www.meditationsuhren.de&lt;/a&gt; pou bay gwo son Bell!</string>
    <string name="about3">&lt;a href="https://github.com/georgernstgraf/zazentimer/issues"&gt;Rapòte pwoblèm sou GitHub&lt;/a&gt;</string>
